<plot>Sleazy impostor, then dance band singer Pertti Ylermi Lindgren merrily re-enacts some of his real-life engagements to 76 different women in the late 1960s. After posing as an aristocrat, educationalist, Italian bank executive, or a priest, "The Count" always manages to escape with the bride's or her father's money just when the wedding bells start to chime.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?297604</url></doc>
